{
  "text": "These findings substantiate the opportunities and threats reported in previous research (see Foltýnek et al. 2020; Kim & Kim 2022; Rahman & Watanobe 2023) regarding AI in education and empirically validates the theoretical perspective perpetuated by TAM that perceived ease of use and perceived usefulness dictate individuals' adoption and use of technology (Marikyan & Papagiannidis 2023).",
  "mask": "(Marikyan & Papagiannidis 2023)",
